title: Charlie's Cafe Bar
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Organic, Beer/Wine, British, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A small cafe with a small choice of vegan choices and a larger choice of gluten free food. All soups are generally vegan (please inquire) and usually one vegan main course is offered. On Sunday serves a vegan breakfast all day. Staff knows what vegan means. Located near the Commandery and less than 60m away from parking.
